outcomeMeasures.title: Number of Chewing Cycles Per Bolus
outcomeMeasures.description: Using surface electromyography (sEMG) of the masseter muscle, we will count the number of muscle contraction spikes (i.e. chewing cycles) seen for chewing activity for a single comfortable bite of each bolus type.
outcomeMeasures.populationDescription: Data for 3 additional participants could not be analyzed due to poor electromyography signal quality.
